{"about_the_game":"Juicy army is the sweetest action roguelike set in a dream universe where you'll have to fight an army of juicy creatures!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features:</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1404800/extras/Scenery.png?t=1622381013\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Discover a world full of delicious treats! This fantasy kingdom is made of sweet and delightful objects! Explore Strawberry Island, Cheese Forest, Candy Land,  Cookie City, Chocolate Realm, and so on.</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1404800/extras/Enemies.png?t=1622381013\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Exotic fruity enemies! There are flying berries, bouncing orange, sniper apple, watermelon bandit, and a lot of other juicy creatures. But don't let their cute appearance fool you! They may look cute, but they can get vicious quickly!</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1404800/extras/Weapons.png?t=1622381013\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> As you progress, you'll find loads of interesting weapons. <br></li><li> Responsive, fluid, and fun to play combat system!<br></li><li> Throughout your journey, you'll unlock new items, each with different strengths. Harness the power of these new abilities and smash through all obstacles!<br></li><li> Beat down powerful bosses.<br></li><li> Procedurally generated worlds blended with handcrafted design elements to keep each run fresh and unique.<br></li><li> Beautiful and adorable art style!</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1404800/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1622381013","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1404800/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1622381013","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1404800/caps